@node "INFO" "SN CallStats v1.1 - Information"
@toc "MAIN"
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
  SN CallStats v1.1 - Information
└─────────────────────────────────┘

A very informative call statistics program designed for inclusion in your
sys.welcome and other areas.

Shows:
  - Caller number for the day.
  - Average number of calls for that day of the week.
  - % the current number is of that average.
  - Highest number of calls for that day of the week.
  - % the highest number was of that average.
  - Statistics and graph for the past seven days.

NOTE:  This is a compiled ARexx script.  However, it does not require any
       additional libraries or RPStart to function (unless otherwise
       noted in these docs).

─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@endnode
